Introduction

Jiyu is a South Korean dancer, singer, and rapper under Starship Entertainment.

She is the leader, lead dancer, sub vocalist and sub rapper of the girl group KiiiKiii, with whom she officially debuted on March 24, 2025 with the release of their first mini album "UNCUT GEM".
